detect magic
Level-1st
CastingTime-1Action
Range/Area-Self
School-Divination
Attack/Save-div
OtherInfo-                For the duration, you sense the resence of magic within 30 feet of you. If you sense magic in this way, you can use your action to see a faint aura around any visible creature or object in the area that bears magic, and you learn its school of magic, if any.
